Discover the Value of CIMA® CertificationAs a CIMA® professional, you will stand out from other investment consultants due to your extensive knowledge of investments, your ability to service more assets for your clients, and your advanced advisor skills. The CIMA certification program is the only credential designed specifically for financial professionals who want to attain a higher level of competency as an advanced investment consultant.Prepare for Your CIMA Certification Exams with KaplanKaplan Financial Education is now recognized as a Certified Investment Management Analyst® (CIMA®) exam prep provider by IMCA®. The certification process consists of 5 steps - trust Kaplan to prepare for Steps 2 and 4, your Qualification and Certification Exams.Kaplan employs a three-phase learning strategy known as Prepare •  Practice • Perform™. Using this scientific model as our foundation, we have constructed the most efficient, effective study products to help you achieve your goal of CIMA® certification. Studying with a Kaplan exam prep package will leave you feeling exam-ready and confident that you will pass your exams on the first try.Select your stage of exam prep below:





